      "message": "I think this is fine while we\u0027re testing this out, but I think it\u0027d be better to not have this restriction long-term. It would be easy for someone to add a crash-key with a colon, which would break all crash-reports containing that key. This wouldn\u0027t necessarily be apparent during development because they key might only be present in certain situations, resulting in crash reports somewhat quietly disappearing.",
